Firstly run command "npm start" from terminal
then you can go through routes
First you have to register a user
Secondly you can login from authenticated username
The next routes can only be used if user has logged in
A user can see all notes, completed notes and incompleted notes from respective routes
User can also changestatus of note, delete note or can add a new note
The authentication is done via express sessions
For data storage, MongoDb is used
And lastly for server purpose and backend API express framework is used.
